que landscapes</strong> depicting the magic of the country throughout the map.<br></li><li><strong>Discover the Slavic folklore</strong> behind FibreTigre\u2019s writing (<i>Out There</i>, <i>Game of R\u00f4les</i>).<br></li><li>The <strong>hand-drawn art style</strong> of Quentin Vijoux will immerse you even more in the universe.</li></ul>","achievements":{"highlighted":[{"name":"The Hero's Journey","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/1633860/094fa8004f6fa44a479cc8d27d48508d532018da.jpg"},{"name":"The Land of Men","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/1633860/c92e0ba1365d8fe1da51473ef0bb7386e8ad62bb.jpg"},{"name":"The Road of Bones","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/1633860/efdaa11554a180e906096d406ea18dd86e50cc16.jpg"},{"name":"The King is Dead, Long Live the King","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/1633860/1e9b9408271e3abdf6edb53b442de297d59ea61c.jpg"},{"name":"Chernobog","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/1633860/8896f81932ca77a8eeea59371db467e727eee3e3.jpg"},{"name":"Hybrid Engine","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/1633860/25142cf973b6ca86894c7f9ff626b785172430a3.jpg"},{"name":"Without a Scratch","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/1633860/93b43f752e596dcf75997431530139b94d3b2de3.jpg"},{"name":"Friend in the North","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/1633860/de07d73efc3e0f8a62aa06b5e722873d8e4c5db6.jpg"},{"name":"Plant Botanist","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/1633860/5735ba539749b55f04416a044431576eb65d744e.jpg"},{"name":"Let There Be Light","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/1633860/f79647655f4bccb8a7b9b1be39f0252752cc8a25.jpg"}],"total":13},"backg